title: Tathastu
subTitle: A factory worker's son needs a heart transplant but the hospital will not go ahead with it without paying upfront. So, he is forced to take the law into his own hands to save his sick child.

subTitle: Kumar and Rohit, who are childhood friends, soon turn enemies when Kumar molests Rohit's fiancee out of jealousy. She feels unworthy of Rohit and calls off the wedding.

subTitle: A young woman, conning people to run an orphanage, falls in love with a rich man under the disguise of a princess. However, their romance crumbles when her truth comes out.

subTitle: The newest compilation of preppy Punjabi music is played continuously for the viewers with a preference for Indian dance beats.

subTitle: Raja, a young man, wants an easy life and marries for wealth and comfort. He soon finds out that there is an underlying secret of his wife and feels trapped.

subTitle: Amar, a rich businessman, is framed by two undercover police officers, Seema and Jagmohan, for the murder of his uncle. To evade prison, he claims to be of unsound mind and tries to solve the mystery.

subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

subTitle: Two siblings, Radha and Ramu, belong to a poor family. Their life takes an unexpected turn when a tragic incident leaves them orphaned.

subTitle: Shaamu, who lives a carefree life, falls in love with a well-educated girl, Raadha. However, circumstances force the young couple to part ways.

title: Vishwanath
subTitle: Vishwanath, an honest lawyer, is framed and imprisoned due to a gangster. After his release, he sets out to seek revenge and ends up becoming a criminal.

title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Accident on Hill Road
subTitle: Sonam's night of celebration turns into a disaster when her car hits an innocent man. Afraid of being punished for the crime, she decides to hide him but invites trouble in turn.
